trelleborg take larger slice of boliden
    stockholm, march 5 - 
swedish tyres, process equipment and components firm <trelleborg ab>
said it was taking a larger stake in mining and metals concern boliden
ab <blds.st> than it had originally intended. trelleborg had
previously announced it was exercising an option to acquire up to 65
pct of boliden's voting rights. in a statement, the company said they
had received offers of up to 68 pct of the rights, and that they would
accept all. reuter 
